        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Overdose Review Team Act</strong></p> <p>This bill provides funding to the Department of Health and Human Services for grants that support drug overdose fatality review teams in states, Indian tribes, territories, and localities. These multidisciplinary teams track fatal and nonfatal drug overdoses that occur in the jurisdiction to identify relevant trends and patterns and recommend policies and practices for preventing and reducing drug overdoses.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
